3.1.3.1 Data Cleaning¶

In [13]:
for i in range(len(data)):
    if pd.isnull(data['hc'].values[i]) and pd.notnull(
            data['nox'].values[i]) and pd.notnull(data['hcnox'].values[i]):
        data['hc'].values[i] = data['hcnox'].values[i] - data['nox'].values[i]
    elif pd.isnull(data['nox'].values[i]) and pd.notnull(
            data['hc'].values[i]) and pd.notnull(data['hcnox'].values[i]):
        data['nox'].values[i] = data['hcnox'].values[i] - data['hc'].values[i]
    elif pd.isnull(data['hcnox'].values[i]) and pd.notnull(
            data['nox'].values[i]) and pd.notnull(data['hc'].values[i]):
           data['hcnox'].values[i] = data['hc'].values[i] + data['nox'].values[i]
            
data.dropna(subset=['hc', 'nox', 'hcnox'], how='all', inplace=True)

Hcnox=Hc+nox, I created a loop and filled in the missing values. I deleted the empty lines in every 3 lines.

In [14]:
for i in range(len(data)):
    if 'V .' in str(data['typ_boite_nb_rapp'].values[i]):
        data['typ_boite_nb_rapp'].values[i] = data['typ_boite_nb_rapp'].values[i].replace('V .', 'V 0')
        
    if 'COMBISPCACE' in str(data['Carrosserie'].values[i]):
        data['Carrosserie'].values[i] = data['Carrosserie'].values[i].replace('COMBISPCACE', 'COMBISPACE')
        
    if 'MOY-INFERIEURE' in str(data['gamme'].values[i]):
        data['gamme'].values[i] = data['gamme'].values[i].replace('MOY-INFERIEURE', 'MOY-INFER')

In [15]:
for i in range(len(data)):
    if '"' in str(data['champ_v9'].values[i]):
        data['champ_v9'].values[i] = data['champ_v9'].values[i].replace('"', '')

    if 'EURO' not in str(data['champ_v9'].values[i]) and '74EEV' not in str(
            data['champ_v9'].values[i]):
        data['champ_v9'].values[i] = 'null'

    if str(data['champ_v9'].values[i][-4:]) == "EURO":
        data['champ_v9'].values[i] = 'null'
data = data.replace('null', np.nan)
data.dropna(subset=['champ_v9'], inplace=True)
